"`PolicyServer`.\n"
"\n"
"| Y\n"
"| `module`\n"
"| The location of the {short-project-name} policy. The following schemes are "
"allowed:\n"
"\n"
"| N\n"
"|\n"
"| - `registry`: Policy download from an\n"
"    https://github.com/opencontainers/artifacts[OCI artifacts] compliant\n"
